@startuml
[*] --> Initial

Initial --> AddingEmployees : new recruitment
AddingEmployees --> ManagingDealers : add or change dealer

ManagingDealers --> LoadingProducts : products loaded
LoadingProducts --> ProductApproval : employee update requires approval

ProductApproval --> SMSAlert : fire detected by camera
SMSAlert --> DeletingFootage : delete old or unnecessary footage

DeletingFootage --> AdjustingPrices : adjust retail prices
AdjustingPrices --> ViewingData : view profit or loss data
ViewingData --> PlacingOrders : place orders from dealers
PlacingOrders --> ReviewingSuggestions : review customer suggestions

@enduml
